name: Guardian Ultra-Short U.S. T-Bill Fund
longDescription: The fund is to provide interest income to unitholders primarily through exposure to short term treasury bills issued by the federal government of the United States with remaining maturities of three months or less. The investment objective of Guardian UltraShort U.S. TBill Fund is to provide interest income to unitholders.
